stunts, pranks, and wackiness!! Watch "Poo Handles", "Bum Interview",
"The Drink", "Hit By Car", and a number of other memorable moments

please do not attempt anything you see, as you may end up injured or
dead. As one reviewer said, "There is some stuff on here they wouldn&#039;t
